OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777551071
OL,3,CDriver who rammed car off road admits
OL,4,Cmanslaughter
OL,6,FA driver who killed a man by
OL,7,Fdeliberately ramming another car off
OL,8,Fthe road has pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Fmanslaughter.
OL,11,FOwen Cocksedge, 19, was behind the
OL,12,Fwheel of a Subaru Forester which
OL,13,Fcollided with a Land Rover Discovery
OL,14,Fon Morthen Road in Rotherham in June
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FMackenzie Ball, who was 20 and a
OL,18,Fpassenger in the Land Rover, died at
OL,19,Fthe scene.
OL,21,FCocksedge fled on foot.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777551071
OL,3,CDriver who rammed car off road admits
OL,4,Cmanslaughter
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the
OL,7,Fincident happened after a fight.
OL,9,FCocksedge pleaded guilty to charges of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter and two counts of
OL,11,Fwounding when he appeared at Sheffield
OL,12,FCrown Court and will be sentenced at a
OL,13,Flater date.
OL,15,FDet Insp Matt Bolger said: "Mackenzie
OL,16,Fwas a young man who had his whole life
OL,17,Fahead of him and since his death, my
OL,18,Fthoughts have been with his family and
OL,19,Ffriends.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777551071
OL,3,CDriver who rammed car off road admits
OL,4,Cmanslaughter
OL,6,F"We have worked around the clock to
OL,7,Fbuild up a picture of what happened in
OL,8,Fthe lead-up to Mackenzie's death, and
OL,9,Fto find those who were involved.
OL,11,F"My deepest condolences remain with
OL,12,FMackenzie's loved ones - their
OL,13,Fpatience and dignity throughout this
OL,14,Finvestigation has been remarkable."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
